rows.name: You didn't make it in time?

rows.label: bf11440100_0030
rows.name: Was that the child from that house?

rows.label: bf11440100_0040
rows.name:
That soldier... wasn't
he the one you...?

The Holy See of Acedia houses
many paintings of hell.

rows.label: bf11440100_0080

But maybe the real thing is
surprisingly mundane, just like this.

rows.label: bf11440100_0100
rows.name:
The salvation of humanity...
It is willed...
